---
import ToolLayout from '../../../layouts/ToolLayout.astro';
---
<ToolLayout
  title="文字数カウンター | X投稿文字数・行数・URL数を同時確認"
  description="文字数、空白抜き文字数、行数、段落数、URL数、UTF-8バイト数、X投稿用のweighted countをリアルタイムで確認できます。"
  canonical="https://www.randaworks.com/tools/moji-counter/"
  pageType="char_counter"
  source="moji_counter"
  tag="X投稿対応"
  heading="文字数カウンター"
  desc="通常の文字数だけでなく、X投稿向けのweighted countや残り文字数も同時に確認できます。"
  breadcrumbs={[
    { href: '/history-tools/', label: 'ツール集' },
    { label: '文字数カウンター' },
  ]}
  excludeTools={['moji-counter']}
  gamePitch="説明文や紹介文の文字量を整えると、ゲームの投稿や告知も読みやすくなります。"
  steamContext="日本史因果クロニクル — 投稿文の長さを整える告知支援ツール"
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net" />
  </Fragment>

  <div class="tool-workspace">
    <div class="tool-output counter-note" style="min-height:auto;margin-bottom:14px;">
      <span class="tool-output-label">できること</span>
      <p>通常文字数、空白抜き文字数、行数、段落数、URL数、UTF-8バイト数、読了目安をリアルタイムで表示します。</p>
      <p>X の文字数は weighted count で計算し、URL は 23 文字換算、返信先頭メンション除外にも対応します。</p>
    </div>

    <div class="tool-chips" id="counterExamples">
      <button type="button" data-text="関ヶ原の戦いで徳川家康が勝利した。">短文</button>
      <button type="button" data-text="新作の体験版を公開しました。遊んだ感想をぜひ教えてください。 https://www.randaworks.com/games/inga/">URL入り投稿</button>
      <button type="button" data-text="@user1 @user2 ご感想ありがとうございます。アップデート内容をまとめました。">返信風</button>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-bottom: 14px;">
      <label for="counterInput" style="display:block; margin-bottom: 6px; color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.92rem;">テキストを入力</label>
      <textarea id="counterInput" rows="10" placeholder="ここに文章を入力してください" style="width:100%;min-height:220px;padding:14px;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);color:#fff;font:inherit;resize:vertical;"></textarea>
    </div>

    <div class="counter-controls">
      <label class="counter-check">
        <input id="xReplyMode" type="checkbox" />
        <span>Xの返信として計算する</span>
      </label>
      <label class="counter-custom-limit">
        <span>任意上限</span>
        <input id="customLimit" type="number" min="1" step="1" value="1000" />
      </label>
      <button class="tool-btn tool-btn-ghost" type="button" id="counterClearBtn">クリア</button>
      <button class="tool-btn tool-btn-ghost" type="button" id="counterCopyBtn">本文をコピー</button>
    </div>

    <section class="counter-grid" id="counterPrimary">
      <article class="counter-card counter-card-emphasis">
        <span class="tool-output-label">通常文字数</span>
        <strong id="countGraphemes">0</strong>
        <span>見た目の文字単位</span>
      </article>
      <article class="counter-card counter-card-emphasis">
        <span class="tool-output-label">X weighted count</span>
        <strong id="countXWeighted">0</strong>
        <span id="countXState">標準投稿 280字まで</span>
      </article>
      <article class="counter-card">
        <span class="tool-output-label">空白抜き</span>
        <strong id="countNoSpaces">0</strong>
        <span>改行・空白を除外</span>
      </article>
      <article class="counter-card">
        <span class="tool-output-label">行数</span>
        <strong id="countLines">0</strong>
        <span>改行単位</span>
      </article>
      <article class="counter-card">
        <span class="tool-output-label">段落数</span>
        <strong id="countParagraphs">0</strong>
        <span>空行区切り</span>
      </article>
      <article class="counter-card">
        <span class="tool-output-label">URL数</span>
        <strong id="countUrls">0</strong>
        <span id="countUrlReserved">Xでは0文字予約</span>
      </article>
      <article class="counter-card">
        <span class="tool-output-label">単語数</span>
        <strong id="countWords">0</strong>
        <span>英語中心の語数</span>
      </article>
      <article class="counter-card">
        <span class="tool-output-label">UTF-8バイト数</span>
        <strong id="countBytes">0</strong>
        <span>APIや保存サイズ確認向け</span>
      </article>
      <article class="counter-card">
        <span class="tool-output-label">読了目安</span>
        <strong id="countReading">0秒</strong>
        <span>日本語500字/分、英語200語/分</span>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section class="counter-grid counter-grid-limits">
      <article class="counter-card limit-card">
        <span class="tool-output-label">X 標準</span>
        <strong id="limitXStandard">残り 280</strong>
        <span>weighted countで計算</span>
      </article>
      <article class="counter-card limit-card">
        <span class="tool-output-label">X 長文</span>
        <strong id="limitXLong">残り 4000</strong>
        <span>長文投稿の目安</span>
      </article>
      <article class="counter-card limit-card">
        <span class="tool-output-label">Instagram</span>
        <strong id="limitInstagram">残り 2200</strong>
        <span>キャプション上限</span>
      </article>
      <article class="counter-card limit-card">
        <span class="tool-output-label">LINE</span>
        <strong id="limitLine">残り 500</strong>
        <span>メッセージ目安</span>
      </article>
      <article class="counter-card limit-card">
        <span class="tool-output-label">Meta Description</span>
        <strong id="limitMeta">残り 160</strong>
        <span>SEO用目安</span>
      </article>
      <article class="counter-card limit-card">
        <span class="tool-output-label">任意上限</span>
        <strong id="limitCustom">残り 1000</strong>
        <span>自由に設定</span>
      </article>
    </section>
  </div>

  <div class="tool-rich-section">
    <section class="tool-output" style="min-height:auto;">
      <h2>使い方</h2>
      <ol class="tool-rich-list">
        <li>本文を貼り付けると、文字数やURL数がリアルタイムで更新されます。</li>
        <li>X投稿を作るときは `X weighted count` と `X 標準` の残り文字数を見ます。</li>
        <li>返信文なら `Xの返信として計算する` をオンにすると、先頭メンションを除外して確認できます。</li>
      </ol>
    </section>
  </div>

  <script type="module" is:inline>
    let twitterTextPromise = null;
    const URL_LENGTH = 23;
    const LIMITS = {
      xStandard: 280,
      xLong: 4000,
      instagram: 2200,
      line: 500,
      meta: 160
    };

    const encoder = new TextEncoder();
    const graphemeSegmenter = typeof Intl !== 'undefined' && Intl.Segmenter
      ? new Intl.Segmenter('ja', { granularity: 'grapheme' })
      : null;
    const wordSegmenter = typeof Intl !== 'undefined' && Intl.Segmenter
      ? new Intl.Segmenter('ja', { granularity: 'word' })
      : null;

    function $(id) { return document.getElementById(id); }

    function track(name, payload) {
      if (window.RandaAnalytics && typeof window.RandaAnalytics.track === 'function') {
        window.RandaAnalytics.track(name, payload || {});
      }
      if (typeof gtag === 'function') {
        gtag('event', name, payload || {});
      }
    }

    function getTwitterText() {
      if (!twitterTextPromise) {
        twitterTextPromise = import('https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/twitter-text@3.1.0/+esm')
          .catch(() => null);
      }
      return twitterTextPromise;
    }

    function getGraphemes(text) {
      if (!text) return [];
      if (graphemeSegmenter) {
        return Array.from(graphemeSegmenter.segment(text), (item) => item.segment);
      }
      return Array.from(text);
    }

    function countWords(text) {
      if (!text.trim()) return 0;
      if (wordSegmenter) {
        return Array.from(wordSegmenter.segment(text)).filter((item) => item.isWordLike).length;
      }
      const matches = text.trim().match(/[^\s]+/g);
      return matches ? matches.length : 0;
    }

    function findUrls(text) {
      const matches = text.match(/https?:\/\/[^\s]+|www\.[^\s]+/gi);
      return matches || [];
    }

    function isEmoji(grapheme) {
      return /\p{Extended_Pictographic}/u.test(grapheme);
    }

    function isWideXChar(grapheme) {
      return /[\p{Script=Han}\p{Script=Hiragana}\p{Script=Katakana}\p{Script=Hangul}]/u.test(grapheme);
    }

    function stripReplyMentions(text) {
      return text.replace(/^(?:\s*@[\w_]{1,15})+\s*/u, '');
    }

    function fallbackXCount(text, replyMode) {
      let source = text.normalize('NFC');
      if (replyMode) {
        source = stripReplyMentions(source);
      }

      const urlRegex = /https?:\/\/[^\s]+|www\.[^\s]+/gi;
      let weighted = 0;
      let cursor = 0;
      let match;

      while ((match = urlRegex.exec(source)) !== null) {
        const before = source.slice(cursor, match.index);
        getGraphemes(before).forEach((grapheme) => {
          if (isEmoji(grapheme) || isWideXChar(grapheme)) {
            weighted += 2;
          } else {
            weighted += 1;
          }
        });
        weighted += URL_LENGTH;
        cursor = match.index + match[0].length;
      }

      const tail = source.slice(cursor);
      getGraphemes(tail).forEach((grapheme) => {
        if (isEmoji(grapheme) || isWideXChar(grapheme)) {
          weighted += 2;
        } else {
          weighted += 1;
        }
      });

      return {
        weightedLength: weighted,
        valid: weighted <= LIMITS.xStandard
      };
    }

    async function getXMetrics(text, replyMode) {
      const lib = await getTwitterText();
      const source = replyMode ? stripReplyMentions(text) : text;
      const parseTweet = lib && (lib.parseTweet || (lib.default && lib.default.parseTweet));
      if (typeof parseTweet === 'function') {
        return parseTweet(source);
      }
      return fallbackXCount(source, false);
    }

    function formatRemaining(limit, current) {
      const remaining = limit - current;
      return '残り ' + remaining.toLocaleString();
    }

    function formatReadingTime(text, words, graphemesNoSpace) {
      const latinWords = words;
      const japaneseChars = (text.match(/[\p{Script=Han}\p{Script=Hiragana}\p{Script=Katakana}]/gu) || []).length;
      const seconds = Math.ceil((japaneseChars / 500 + latinWords / 200) * 60);
      if (seconds <= 0) return '0秒';
      if (seconds < 60) return seconds + '秒';
      const min = Math.floor(seconds / 60);
      const sec = seconds % 60;
      return sec ? min + '分' + sec + '秒' : min + '分';
    }

    function updateCounterCard(id, value) {
      const el = $(id);
      if (el) el.textContent = value;
    }

    function updateLimitCard(id, current, limit) {
      const el = $(id);
      if (!el) return;
      el.textContent = formatRemaining(limit, current);
      el.classList.toggle('over-limit', current > limit);
    }

    async function recalc() {
      const text = $('counterInput').value || '';
      const replyMode = $('xReplyMode').checked;
      const customLimit = Math.max(1, Number($('customLimit').value || 1000));

      const graphemes = getGraphemes(text);
      const noSpaces = getGraphemes(text.replace(/\s/gu, ''));
      const lines = text ? text.split(/\r\n|\r|\n/).length : 0;
      const paragraphs = text.trim() ? text.trim().split(/\n\s*\n/).length : 0;
      const urls = findUrls(text);
      const words = countWords(text);
      const bytes = encoder.encode(text).length;
      const xResult = await getXMetrics(text, replyMode);
      const xWeighted = Number(xResult && xResult.weightedLength ? xResult.weightedLength : 0);

      updateCounterCard('countGraphemes', graphemes.length.toLocaleString());
      updateCounterCard('countNoSpaces', noSpaces.length.toLocaleString());
      updateCounterCard('countLines', lines.toLocaleString());
      updateCounterCard('countParagraphs', paragraphs.toLocaleString());
      updateCounterCard('countUrls', urls.length.toLocaleString());
      updateCounterCard('countWords', words.toLocaleString());
      updateCounterCard('countBytes', bytes.toLocaleString());
      updateCounterCard('countXWeighted', xWeighted.toLocaleString());
      updateCounterCard('countReading', formatReadingTime(text, words, noSpaces.length));
      updateCounterCard('countXState', replyMode ? '返信先頭メンション除外' : '標準投稿 280字まで');
      updateCounterCard('countUrlReserved', 'Xでは ' + (urls.length * URL_LENGTH).toLocaleString() + '文字予約');

      updateLimitCard('limitXStandard', xWeighted, LIMITS.xStandard);
      updateLimitCard('limitXLong', xWeighted, LIMITS.xLong);
      updateLimitCard('limitInstagram', graphemes.length, LIMITS.instagram);
      updateLimitCard('limitLine', graphemes.length, LIMITS.line);
      updateLimitCard('limitMeta', graphemes.length, LIMITS.meta);
      updateLimitCard('limitCustom', graphemes.length, customLimit);
    }

    function init() {
      const input = $('counterInput');
      const clearBtn = $('counterClearBtn');
      const copyBtn = $('counterCopyBtn');
      const replyMode = $('xReplyMode');
      const customLimit = $('customLimit');
      const chips = document.querySelectorAll('[data-text]');

      input.addEventListener('input', recalc);
      replyMode.addEventListener('change', recalc);
      customLimit.addEventListener('input', recalc);

      clearBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
        input.value = '';
        recalc();
      });

      copyBtn.addEventListener('click', async () => {
        if (!input.value) return;
        await navigator.clipboard.writeText(input.value);
      });

      chips.forEach((chip) => {
        chip.addEventListener('click', () => {
          input.value = chip.getAttribute('data-text') || '';
          recalc();
        });
      });

      recalc();
      input.addEventListener('blur', () => {
        if (input.value.trim()) {
          track('moji_counter_use', { length: input.value.length });
        }
      });
    }

    if (document.readyState === 'loading') {
      document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', init, { once: true });
    } else {
      init();
    }
  </script>

  <style is:inline>
    .counter-note p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .counter-note {
      display: grid;
      gap: 6px;
    }

    .counter-controls {
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .counter-check,
    .counter-custom-limit {
      display: inline-flex;
      gap: 8px;
      align-items: center;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .counter-custom-limit input {
      width: 100px;
      padding: 8px 10px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      color: #fff;
      font: inherit;
    }

    .counter-grid {
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(170px, 1fr));
    }

    .counter-grid + .counter-grid {
      margin-top: 14px;
    }

    .counter-card {
      display: grid;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 16px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
    }

    .counter-card strong {
      color: #fff;
      font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
      line-height: 1.1;
    }

    .counter-card span:last-child {
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .counter-card-emphasis {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(87,164,212,0.16), rgba(255,255,255,0.03));
      border-color: rgba(87,164,212,0.26);
    }

    .limit-card strong {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }

    .over-limit {
      color: #ff8f8f;
    }
  </style>
</ToolLayout>
